There are just some usability issues which can leave you disappointed if you aren't prepared for them. Purchasing this app doesn't create an account. If you want to share workouts etc with someone using an iPhone ... prepare to be disappointed because you get a notification that says you cant share between Android and iOS when you go to import the file. The models, exercise demonstrations and information tracked is nicely done. So the app is useful, but annoying at the same time. Having bought it, it will now simply collect dust unless I want to look at the 3D models or take inspiration from the exercises.
